FT  12 MAY 92 / Observer: Open arms
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
The prime minister's bid for more open government clearly has some way to go
when it comes to arms sales. Last year John Major strongly backed plans for
a UN register on which all significant exports of weapons would be declared.
But the Ministry of Defence was not keen to advertise last Friday's arrival
