past three years and hasn't finished spending. Having been spirited off to a
helicopter show in Middle Wallop, the visitor and his plans to meet
ministers and industry had to be acknowledged - albeit 12 hours later.
Memo to Britain's top brass: to keep such visits secret, urge the customer
not to arrive on the same flight from Jakarta as the Duchess of York.
